name: Cowboy Go!
description:
Cowboy Go!  is a casual cowboy game! Use lasso to catch more animals, control the crazy cowboy in his adventure! 
Ducks? Rabbits? Birds? Monkeys? Cowboys are not vaquero or pet sitters in pink, they are going to catch cheetahs, lions, elephants, hippos, they are trying to challenge lion king, unicorns, dinosaurs, king kong, even dragons and monsters! Welcome to this fantastic wild west!  PS. No Godzilla here, sorry.
Catch golden bulls and other golden animals to get bounty, buy yourself new horses, saddles, and cowboy hats!
Tired to ride horses? No problem! You can raid everything you caught! Just need pay little love on it.
Fishing Games are old school. Play cowboy game now!
Be a Real Cowboy! Enjoy your fantastic wild west life!
